Class EnumT

java.lang.Object
  xtc.tree.Node
      xtc.type.Type
          xtc.type.WrappedT
              xtc.type.EnumT
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<Object>, Locatable, Tagged
public class EnumT
extends WrappedT
implements Tagged

An enumerated type. Note that the list of members for an enumerated type is the list of enumerators.

Version:
$Revision: 1.40 $
